Class DefectChangeset

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.AbstractModel

        • edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.defecttracker.models.DefectChangeset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Model

    public class DefectChangeset
extends DefectEvent
    Persistent Model that holds information about a set of changes to a Defect. Every time a Defect is changed by a user, a DefectChangeset should be created containing the changes and the user responsible for making them.
